System Minimum Requirements (or equivalent) (or better):

CPU: Intel® Core™ i3-1005G1/AMD Ryzen 3 3200U
RAM: 6 GB
VIDEO CARD: Intel® UHD Graphics/Radeon Vega graphics
VRAM: 1 GB
OS: Windows 10/11 64-bit
Storage: 5GB
(An internet connection is required for online play.)

